collection.name: The Walking Dead Official
collection.description:
##The Official AMC’s The Walking Dead Walker Access Pass NFT

See our [Special Gold Auction 1:1 Collection here](https://opensea.io/collection/thewalkingdeadofficialauction)

These passes will grant the holder a White List Access for all of our future AMC TWD drops, access to Exclusive The Walking Dead Drops (5 per year) and much more. Each Walker Access Pass will feature one of ten different 3D Walkers set in a variety of backgrounds. The passes will be cloaked at the time of purchase as each will be randomly minted. For each purchase the grand reveal of all passes will take place two weeks after the close of the drop. Each Walker Access Pass will contain over 30 traits. 
For more information [see our roadmap](https://orangecomet.com/collection/the-walking-dead-opensea/).

ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.
